column.name: Query
column.value: "SELECT partc.id as id_prop_participe, partc.identificacao as co_prop_participe FROM siconv.participe partc INNER JOIN siconv.participantes_prop pprop on partc.id = pprop.id LEFT JOIN (SELECT aap.participes_fk, array_to_string( array(SELECT aaet2.descricao FROM siconv.areas_atuacao_participes aap2 INNER JOIN siconv.area_atuacao_enti_privada aaet2 on aaet2.id = aap2.areas_atuacao_fk WHERE aap2.participes_fk = aap.participes_fk), ' / ') as desc_area_atuacao FROM siconv.areas_atuacao_participes aap INNER JOIN siconv.area_atuacao_enti_privada aaet on aaet.id = aap.areas_atuacao_fk GROUP BY aap.participes_fk ) area_atuacao on pprop.id = area_atuacao.participes_fk LEFT JOIN siconv.dsc_enumerados dsc on pprop.esfera_administrativa = dsc.atributo WHERE dsc.dominio='EsferaAdministrativa' "
